Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world are you\Nstill out in this downpour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been several months\Nsince Kagari vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to track down her whereabouts\Nusing all possible means, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we just couldn't locate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the facility Moeka and I found...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never found out exactly what it was for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was... brainwashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have definitive proof though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't explain Kagari's background,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't recruit any police help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if you brought an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain comes out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure has lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's the rainy season. It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's not far off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a life of fantasy,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unaffected still by illusions.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worldlines without end{\i}\N{\i1}are all deceived by an antinomy paradox{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can dominate these emotions,{\i}\N{\i1}orbital ordering replacing even common sense,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then my suffering{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}alone{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is the gap to cross in this algorithm{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Signs of love, words of love...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The memories flow back with total clarity{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never again will I forsake what lies beyond,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want always to be by your side, hand-in-hand,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As this quantum entanglement forms Zero{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no God. Wonderful new world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Maho-tan. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyajo-san? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sleepy Maho-tan! What a turn-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're contacting me again,\NI'm guessing... You're actually serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you before, if we end up\Nnot being able to use the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll need the time leap machine for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think it's doable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it to the point before Okarin broke\Nit apart and threw it in the trash, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even close to stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they compress an absurd amount\Nof memory data to be sent into the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you figure that out, it's pointless to—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're here talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't ask Uncle Okarin,\Nyou're our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I can do everything\Njust because I'm a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you had Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had the brains of that genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're a genius in your own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the lip service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a no, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salieri can't compose the songs Mozart did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I... talking to them looking like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... Do you think this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Okarin finds out, he'll be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather convince him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! He'll scrap it as soon as he hears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin's always looks dead\Nserious when he says it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Don't even think about changing the future.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta imagine he's got\Na good reason for saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, I can understand where he's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is letting World War III and\Nthis worldline happen the right choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Okarin would agree with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why won't he take action?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got the time machine\Nhe needs to find Steins Gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got the ability to remember other\Nworldlines through Reading Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why has he given up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't he at least try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, someday Okarin's going to be\Nreborn and go all “Mwahahahaha!” like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been saying that for over half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't count on Uncle Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I said you could leave it to me,\Nand now look where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how hard you've been\Npushing yourself, if only for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Mayu-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says Fubuki-shi is back in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom will be there, right? Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time to be concerned about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what if it ends up with me not being born?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will not let you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii! Okarin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki-chan, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine! So get this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just asked me to come back\Nto the hospital again for another exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And silly Kaede-chan here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Fubuki-chan sent a message saying\Nshe'd be in the hospital for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said a little while, didn't I? Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's no need to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin! Mayu-shi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Didn't Fubuki-shi collapse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why does everyone\Nneed their own private room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's a necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you keep saying,\Nbut I don't think it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then find a way to make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Leskinen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lintahlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor? You know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He's the world's third Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lintahlo here will be transferring\Nto my university in September,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll eventually have him\Njoin my research team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Viktor Chondria University?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no. That is my ultimate goal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-shi, Mayu-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin's transferring overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the fact that you're able\Nto study overseas is impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's set in stone yet,\Nbut Okarin's doing his best to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The hospital director?\NYou lied to someone that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie to anyone, Lintahlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I might have told him September...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say of which year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hiyajo-san here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curious, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, she's back in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I will tell her that\Nyou were asking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, the only\Nreasonable assumption is that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they sent the memory data\Nsomewhere to be compressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the places she's\Naffiliated with capable of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, make one wrong move\Nand you'd be disgracing the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong move and\Nthis will turn out nearly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. The professor's in Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he must've ran into Okabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish you were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, your eyes are bloodshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lack of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he's such a weird guy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, the first thing he asked was\Nif time machines could be built or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think one...\Ncould build... a time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have Makise Kurisu's\Nmemories from spring of last year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before she went off to Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but... Why ask that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if... Suppose if...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you found out a way to make a time machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything needed to make it was\Nright in front of you, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a silly question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who makes it all possible says this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Time machines are the work of the devil.\NThey must never be made.”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see..”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, who knows what happens\Nwhen you interfere with the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would even become of us in the present?\NWe haven't the slightest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I would put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using it or not would be the tough choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She dropped this half a year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go rinse myself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try anything funny, I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And slowly walk toward the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot and yet you\Ncan stand wearing that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take off that helmet of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the voice of God...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kagari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The precious gift... Mommy gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe you're the same girl\Nwho was always bawling in the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Mayu... was crying, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy... was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha, what's up?\NYou left the door wide open...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and hurt my Dad if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now... that was Kagari-tan... wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kagari-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see, Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... she was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you should go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I just got grazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the woman in\Nthe motorcycle suit was Kagari-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person that attacked\Nyou guys was somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it happened,\NKagari would've been at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... Uncle Okarin's\Nguess was right in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari was brainwashed and\Nis being controlled by somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brainwashed, though? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must've found out Kagari came\Nhere by time machine and captured her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the voice of God...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear... a voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice... of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... At that point,\NKagari was already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a hold of Okarin and\Nlet him know that Kagari-tan showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hears that Kagari is back, he'll probably\Ngo searching for her like crazy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as you just found out,\NKagari is far too dangerous right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if it is brainwashing,\NI might have a hunch or two about Kagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, in order to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Kagari,\Nwe'll have to use the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot! Why did it\Ntake me so long to remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tormented my Valkyrie\Ncomrades one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bureau's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try asking Maho-tan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come here, and seriously get to work\Ndeveloping the time leap machine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes to get\Nit finished, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus if you come, I get to see loli\NMaho-tan in summer clothes! Huff huff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure-white one piece and high socks, yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. My vivid imagination\Ngot the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously now, without you, I'll never\Nbe able to restore the PhoneWave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really intend to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you at least let me think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never pried into the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Makise Kurisu and Okabe Rintaro\Nmust have, in some other worldline,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gone through trial and error over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow, they successfully manipulated time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She succeeded.\NMakise Kurisu built that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it? To get a paper\Npublished at such a young age...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magnificent! Your talent is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the world has acknowledged you,\NI imagine work will get very busy for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prove I could see inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show I could do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, make one wrong move\Nand you'd be disgracing the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... What should I even do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're fine with me, I could lend an ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—[Kurisu]! Help me find something! An old magazine!\N—Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um... Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can find my way there all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not by searching through\Nyour work for all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by going down that same path...\Nand reaching it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I will head back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the city where Makise Kurisu's life ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason itself is\Nhard to put into words, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:22:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, if I had to give an answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one person who acknowledged\NMozart's talent above anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Salieri.
